products.title: ZOTAC Gaming GeForce RTX 2080 Super Triple Fan 8GB GDDR6 256-bit 15.5Gbps Gaming Graphics Card, IceStorm 2.0, Active Fan Control, ZT-T20820H-10P
features: Turing Architecture, Ray Tracing Cores, Tensor Cores, NVIDIA DLSS
IceStorm 2.0, our strongest cooling, Active Fan Control, die-cast metal PCB brace add structural stenghthening, Metal Wraparound Backplate
products.description:
Everything is super with the all-new ZOTAC GAMING GeForce RTX 20 Series SUPER graphics cards. Based on the NVIDIA Turing architecture, it’s packed with more cores and ultra-fast GDDR6 memory. Integrated with more smart and optimized technologies, get ready to GET FAST and GAME STRONG.

FEATURES
• IceStorm 2.0 Cooling
• Active Fan Control
• Wraparound Metal Backplate
• Real-time Ray Tracing and DLSS support
• 4K, VR and HDR Ready
• NVIDIA Ansel
• NVIDIA G-SYNC compatible
• NVLink (SLI-ready)

SPECIFICATIONS
• NVIDIA GeForce RTX 2080 SUPER GPU
• 3072 CUDA cores
• 8GB GDDR6 memory
• 256-bit memory bus
• Engine boost clock: 1815 MHz
• Memory clock: 15.5 Gbps
• PCI Express 3.0

CONNECTIONS
• 3 x DisplayPort 1.4 (up to 7680x4320@60Hz)
• HDMI 2.0b (up to 3840x2160@60Hz)
• Quad simultaneous display capable

SOFTWARE COMPATIBILITY
• Game Ready Drivers
• Microsoft DirectX 12 API, Vulkan API
• OpenGL 4.5
• Microsoft Windows 10/7 64-bit, Linux 64-bit

POWER REQUIREMENTS
• 650-watt power supply recommended
• 250-watt max power consumption

INSIDE THE BOX
• ZOTAC GAMING GeForce RTX 2080 SUPER Triple Fan
• Dual 6-pin to 8-pin cable
• Dual 4-pin to 6-pin cable
• User Manual

DIMENSIONS
• Length: 308mm (12.13in)
• Height: 113mm (4.45in)
• Width: 2.5 slots (57mm) (2.24in)
• Box
• Height: 424mm (16.69in)
• Width: 292mm (11.50in)
• Depth: 99mm (3.90in)
